<h1>About StudyMates</h1>

<p>
	StudyMates is a collaborative platform built to bring students and professionals together in a simple and effective way. Our goal is to make learning more engaging by enabling users to connect, share knowledge, and support each other.
</p>


<p>
	We believe that studying is more productive when done together. Whether you're preparing for exams, working on projects, or learning new concepts, StudyMates helps you find the right people to learn with.
</p>

<p>
	This project focuses on simplicity, usability, and meaningful connections among students and professionals.
</p>